# <%@meta name="title"%>

This report benchmark the performance of <%=fcnname%>() against alternative methods.

## Alternative methods

* apply() + sd()
* colSdColMeans()

where

```r
<%=withCapture({
colSdColMeans <- function(x, na.rm=TRUE) {
  if (na.rm) {
    n <- colSums(!is.na(x))
  } else {
    n <- nrow(x)
  }
  var <- colMeans(x*x, na.rm=na.rm) - (colMeans(x, na.rm=na.rm))^2
  sqrt(var * n/(n-1))
}
})%>
```

See also [StackOverflow:colSds?].


## Data
```r
<%=withCapture({
<%@include file="R/random-matrices.R"%>
